<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4649364>
        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Fig. 1. Micoletzkyia mawatarii sp. nov., holotype, ZIHU 4073 (A–C, E–G) and paratypes, ZIHU 4075 (D) and ZIHU 4077 (H). A, anterior region of male body; B, head of male; C, posterior region of male body; D, posterior region of female body; E, reproductive system of male (testes and vas deferens); F, distal end of spicules and gubernaculum at cloacal region of male; G, precloacal supplement of male; H, reproductive system of female (ovaries, uterus, eggs, and vulva). Scale bars: A, E, H, 200µm; B, 10µm; C, D, 100µm; F, 10µm; G, 20µm." ;
        fabio:hasRepresentation  "https://zenodo.org/record/4649364/files/figure.png" .
